											<span id="DataList1__ctl0_Label1"><font face="Verdana" size="1"><P>I just got finished putting a bandaid on the forums login.&nbsp; It wont kick you back to the login after you login, which was pretty annoying :)&nbsp; Now it will send you back to where ever you clicked the login button.&nbsp; Don`t get me wrong, the board did that before but I broke it by making my changes a few days ago.</P>
<P>As much as I didn`t want to, it looks like I am going to have to make my own forum.&nbsp; The one I am using now is great, I really like it.. its just not meant to do what I need for guildwizard.&nbsp; I own the source for it, but its in Visual Basic, a language that I *can* program in, but my god I hate programming in vb.&nbsp; Also, I am thinking by the time I get it the way I like , i could have just did it from scratch.. well not really, but you get the picture.&nbsp; </P>
<P>This wont happen anytime soon, and I am still not sure I will do it at all..&nbsp; Just kicking it around.</P></font></span>
