											<span id="DataList1__ctl4_Label1"><font face="Verdana" size="1"><P>I am going to work with the forums a bit as my next project for Guild Wizard.&nbsp; Man it`s getting confusing how each guild is kind of a sub forum of the main forum.&nbsp; I have gotten a few complaints about this, and I agree..&nbsp;&nbsp; </P>
<P>So, I am going to try to make it&nbsp;a LOT more private for each guild.&nbsp; As you might know, I didnt write the forums.. Andrew at <A href="http://www.dotnetbb.com">www.dotnetbb.com</A> did a fantastic job on the forums, but they are not meant for what I have implemented.&nbsp; They can, however, be customized to do what we want them to do at Guild Wizard..atleast I am hoping anyway.</P>
<P>From the start, I didnt want to write my own forum software.&nbsp; I simply don`t have time to do it, and I hate to re-invent the wheel.&nbsp; However, if I can`t get the forums the right way, I will have to do it.&nbsp; I am very confident, though, that I can customize the existing boards the way they should be.</P></font></span>
